%h2 Comments
.comments
  %p Got something to say? Join the conversation below.
  .comment
    .actions.btn-group
      = link_to "/thumbsUp", { class: 'btn', title: 'Like this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-up
        10
      = link_to "/thumbsDown", { class: 'btn', title: 'Disike this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-down
        1
      = link_to "/flag", { class: 'btn', title: 'Flag this comment as inappropriate', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-flag
    %p I wish I could have come up with something better to say here. But this will have to do. Did you also enjoy this? Because I did. Very much so. Thanks so much for this.
    .author
      %span.user= link_to '@user', '/profile/user'
      posted on
      %span.date Jan 1st
      at
      %span.time 4:22pm
  .comment
    .actions.btn-group
      = link_to "/thumbsUp", { class: 'btn btn-success disabled', title: 'You have already liked this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-up.icon-white
        403
      = link_to "/thumbsDown", { class: 'btn', title: 'Disike this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-down
        22
      = link_to "/flag", { class: 'btn', title: 'Flag this comment as inappropriate', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-flag
    %p I wish I could have come up with something better to say here. This is lame.
    .author
      %span.user= link_to '@biggestFan', '/profile/user2'
      posted on
      %span.date Jan 8th
      at
      %span.time 4:01pm
  .comment
    .actions.btn-group
      = link_to "/thumbsUp", { class: 'btn', title: 'Like this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-up
        0
      = link_to "/thumbsDown", { class: 'btn btn-danger disabled', title: 'You have already disliked this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-thumbs-down.icon-white
        83
      = link_to "/flag", { class: 'btn', title: 'Flag this comment as inappropriate', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
        %i.icon-flag
    %p I wish I could have come up with something better to say here. This is lame.
    .author
      %span.user= link_to '@biggestFan', '/profile/user2'
      posted on
      %span.date Jan 8th
      at
      %span.time 4:01pm
  - 2.times do |comment|
    .comment
      .actions.btn-group
        = link_to "/thumbsUp", { class: 'btn', title: 'Like this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
          %i.icon-thumbs-up
          0
        = link_to "/thumbsDown", { class: 'btn', title: 'Disike this comment', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
          %i.icon-thumbs-down
          0
        = link_to "/flag", { class: 'btn', title: 'Flag this comment as inappropriate', data: { toggle: 'tooltip' } } do
          %i.icon-flag
